[5.280859, "o", "\u001b[1;35m━━━ Fresh agent starts — user (Sam) was seen in previous sessions ━━━\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[6.236417, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1;36m🦆 I'm back. What do you remember about me? Retrieve from memory and summarize as a bullet list.\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n"]
[8.81924, "o", "I'll retrieve what I remember about you from memory.\r\nTool #1: agent_core_memory\r\n"]
[12.304508, "o", "Welcome back, Sam! Here's what I remember about you:\r\n\r\n•"]
[12.45722, "o", " **Name:** Sam Johnson\r\n• **Location:** You"]
[12.514055, "o", " live in San Francisco\r\n• **Work"]
[12.69993, "o", ":** You're building agricultural drones for precision farming\r\n• **Programming"]
[12.874843, "o", ":** Your favorite programming language is Python\r\n• **Ho"]
[13.409824, "o", "bbies:** You love sailing on weekends\r\n\r\n\u001b[1;36m🦆 Given what you know, suggest a weekend project idea.\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n"]
[15.728632, "o", "Based on what I know about you, here's a weekend project idea that combines your interests:\r\n\r\n##"]
[16.344198, "o", " **\"SailBot\" - A Sailing Weather & Conditions Analyzer**\r\n\r\nBuild"]
[16.763122, "o", " a Python application that helps optimize your weekend sailing trips by:\r\n\r\n**Core"]
[16.814984, "o", " Features:**\r\n- **"]
[17.438131, "o", "Weather API Integration**: Pull real-time wind speed, direction, and marine forecasts for San Francisco Bay\r\n- **Optimal"]
[17.796844, "o", " Sailing Time Predictor**: Analyze weather patterns to suggest the best sailing windows\r\n- **Route"]
[18.268276, "o", " Visualizer**: Map out sailing routes based on current conditions\r\n\r\n**Why"]
[18.4688, "o", " this fits you:**\r\n- "]
[18.731769, "o", "✅ **Python-based** - uses your favorite language\r\n- ✅ **"]
[19.044196, "o", "Sailing-related** - enhances your weekend hobby\r\n- ✅ **San"]
[19.35684, "o", " Francisco-specific** - tailored to Bay Area sailing conditions\r\n- ✅ **"]
[20.324298, "o", "Drone tech crossover** - you can apply similar sensor data processing and geospatial analysis skills you use with your agricultural drones\r\n\r\n**Bonus"]
[20.418819, "o", " Extension:**\r\nIf"]
[20.633711, "o", " you want to bridge it with your drone work, you could eventually add:\r\n- Wind"]
[20.891877, "o", " pattern visualization similar to agricultural field mapping\r\n- Integration"]
[21.255105, "o", " with small weather sensors (like a mini weather station)\r\n- Computer"]
[21.564091, "o", " vision to analyze Bay conditions from webcam feeds\r\n\r\nThis"]
[22.50575, "o", " project is manageable for a weekend, practical for your hobby, and lets you flex your Python skills while staying in your technical comfort zone! 🚤⚓\r\n\r\nWhat"]
[22.890508, "o", " do you think?"]
[23.034592, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1;33m✓ Facts saved in session A, retrieved after fresh restart in session B.\u001b[0m\r\n"]
